HEADWORD: Squalodon
<hw>Squa"lo*don</hw> <pr>(skw⟦amac⟧"l⟦osl⟧*d⟦ocr⟧n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[NL. <ets>Squalus</ets> a genus of sharks + Gr. <grk>'odoy`s</grk>,
<grk>'odo`ntos</grk>, a tooth.]</ety> <fld>(Paleon.)</fld> <def>A genus
